    <h1 id="title">Johnny Cash</h1>
    <h3>A man that made country music and stood up for the little guy by standing up to the big guy.
         He is a true music iconc and his music will be heard for generations</h3>
         <div class="img-containter" id="img-div">
         <img src="https://api.time.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/glast.jpg"
         alt="johnny"
